2025-09-02T17:41:10:           COUNT(te.id) as entry_count
2025-09-02T17:41:10:         FROM projects p
2025-09-02T17:41:10:         INNER JOIN time_entries te ON p.id = te.project_id 
2025-09-02T17:41:10:         WHERE p.user_id = @userId 
2025-09-02T17:41:10:           AND te.user_id = @userId
2025-09-02T17:41:10:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) >= CONVERT(date, @startDate) 
2025-09-02T17:41:10:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) <= CONVERT(date, @endDate)
2025-09-02T17:41:10:         
2025-09-02T17:41:10:         GROUP BY p.id, p.name
2025-09-02T17:41:10:         ORDER BY SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))) DESC

2025-09-02T17:56:30:         FROM projects p
2025-09-02T17:56:30:         INNER JOIN time_entries te ON p.id = te.project_id 
2025-09-02T17:56:30:         WHERE p.user_id = @userId 
2025-09-02T17:56:30:           AND te.user_id = @userId
2025-09-02T17:56:30:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) >= CONVERT(date, @startDate) 
2025-09-02T17:56:30:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) <= CONVERT(date, @endDate)
2025-09-02T17:56:30:         
2025-09-02T17:56:30:         GROUP BY p.id, p.name
2025-09-02T17:56:30:         ORDER BY SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))) DESC

2025-09-03T07:02:59:         SELECT
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           p.id,
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           p.name,
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           '#1976D2' as color,
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           COALESCE(SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))), 0) as total_hours,
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           COUNT(te.id) as entry_count
2025-09-03T07:02:59:         FROM projects p
2025-09-03T07:02:59:         INNER JOIN time_entries te ON p.id = te.project_id 
2025-09-03T07:02:59:         WHERE p.user_id = @userId 
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           AND te.user_id = @userId
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) >= CONVERT(date, @startDate) 
2025-09-03T07:02:59:           AND CONVERT(date, te.date) <= CONVERT(date, @endDate)
2025-09-03T07:02:59:         
2025-09-03T07:02:59:         GROUP BY p.id, p.name
2025-09-03T07:02:59:         ORDER BY SUM(CAST(te.hours as DECIMAL(10,2))) DESC
